{"tid":2045899,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你哋知唔知陳茂波係靠美軍「契爺」助養架","createTime":"2020-06-01T05:34:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T05:39:22.000Z","uid":24660,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a7c3ce6a19ba0730f470fd7658433e7368fadc1d","tid":2045899,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T05:34:42.000Z","msg":"陳茂波記得，五歲至七歲這段期間，不時跟爸爸來到社工姐姐面前，每次聽她解釋一封英文信，然後把爸爸代擬的回信抄寫好， 便可拿到一點錢。四十多年後，在機緣 巧合下，他終於尋回這一對千里以外的「契爺」和「契娘」。陳茂波很開心，和太太、子女專程飛往美國探望他們。陳茂波發現， 八十歲、滿頭白髮、已經退休的「契爺」 出身並不富裕，五十年前只是一個軍人， 小康家庭，當時「契爺」和「契娘」還要供養自己的子女，但都決定每月省下七美元， 助養一個在太平洋彼岸素未謀面的香港 小朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ceo.gov.hk/archive/2017/chi/pdf/POs_booklet.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ceo.gov.hk%2Farchive%2F2017%2Fchi%2Fpdf%2FPOs_booklet.pdf&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGliy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=1eab5c7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ceo.gov.hk/archive/2017/chi/pdf/POs_booklet.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"0e0c9e43a00367c04e3570d1f74d7c1c07b97e81","tid":2045899,"uid":109462,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T05:37:21.000Z","msg":"美國中情局從小培養潛伏在香港政府高層的高級特務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3712b06d3df59e8b1eaa5b62c229599b54dcb87b","tid":2045899,"uid":8014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T05:37:25.000Z","msg":"勾結外國勢力 過左國安法即時拉得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46205202623cec649de6be4b26b5467d7cf8de22","tid":2045899,"uid":262557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T05:39:22.000Z","msg":"養大狼狗咬春袋"}]}